short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Play Geometry Dash Breeze right in your Chrome browser!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Geometry Dash Breeze is a fast paced rhythm based platformer game based on the original geometry dash. Quick reaction and precise timing is required to jump and avoid spikes, gaps and other obstacles.

With the help of this extension, now you can play Geometry Dash Breeze right in your browser with a single click.

Once you install the extension you can start playing right away. No complicated settings or controls.

If you like games that challenge your timing and reaction, Geometry Dash Breeze is for you.

Geometry Dash Breeze has three levels right now, namely Over the Clouds, Into the Zone, and Ghost Ship.

Feel free to leave a review or share it with friends if you enjoy it. Your feedback helps us improve and make it even better.
